---
// FAQ.astro
---

<div id='faq' class='max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16' x-data='{ active: null }'>
  <h2 class='text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12'>
    Frequently Asked Questions
  </h2>

  <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
  <div class='mb-4'>
    <button
      class='flex justify-between w-full p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50'
      @click='active = active === 1 ? null : 1'
      :class="{ 'mb-2': active === 1 }"
    >
      <span class='font-semibold text-xl'
        >How does your mattress delivery process work?</span
      >
      <svg
        class='w-5 h-5 transition-transform'
        :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 1 }"
        fill='none'
        stroke='currentColor'
        viewBox='0 0 24 24'
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap='round'
          stroke-linejoin='round'
          stroke-width='2'
          d='M19 9l-7 7-7-7'></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
    <div
      x-show='active === 1'
      x-collapse
      x-cloak
      class='px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm'
    >
      <p class='text-gray-600'>
        We offer convenient delivery throughout the Phoenix metro area. Once you
        select your mattress, we'll schedule a delivery time that works for you.
        Our team will bring the mattress directly to your home, set it up in
        your desired room, and remove your old mattress if needed. We aim to
        make the process as seamless as possible!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
  <div class='mb-4'>
    <button
      class='flex justify-between w-full p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50'
      @click='active = active === 2 ? null : 2'
      :class="{ 'mb-2': active === 2 }"
    >
      <span class='font-semibold text-xl'
        >What makes your prices better than retail stores?</span
      >
      <svg
        class='w-5 h-5 transition-transform'
        :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 2 }"
        fill='none'
        stroke='currentColor'
        viewBox='0 0 24 24'
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap='round'
          stroke-linejoin='round'
          stroke-width='2'
          d='M19 9l-7 7-7-7'></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
    <div
      x-show='active === 2'
      x-collapse
      x-cloak
      class='px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm'
    >
      <p class='text-gray-600'>
        We operate with lower overhead costs than traditional retail stores by
        not maintaining expensive showrooms. We work directly with manufacturers
        and have established strong relationships that allow us to get wholesale
        pricing. These savings are passed directly to you, often resulting in
        40-60% off retail prices for the same high-quality mattresses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
  <div class='mb-4'>
    <button
      class='flex justify-between w-full p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50'
      @click='active = active === 3 ? null : 3'
      :class="{ 'mb-2': active === 3 }"
    >
      <span class='font-semibold text-xl'
        >Do you offer warranties on your mattresses?</span
      >
      <svg
        class='w-5 h-5 transition-transform'
        :class="{ 'rotate-180': active === 3 }"
        fill='none'
        stroke='currentColor'
        viewBox='0 0 24 24'
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap='round'
          stroke-linejoin='round'
          stroke-width='2'
          d='M19 9l-7 7-7-7'></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
    <div
      x-show='active === 3'
      x-collapse
      x-cloak
      class='px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm'
    >
      <p class='text-gray-600'>
        Yes! All our mattresses come with full manufacturer warranties,
        typically ranging from 10-20 years depending on the brand and model.
        These warranties cover any manufacturing defects or unusual wear. We'll
        provide you with all warranty documentation upon delivery and are happy
        to assist with any warranty claims if needed.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  [x-cloak] {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>
